    <item>
      <title>拉美航空寻求破产后的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/latam-airlines-is-looking-to-grow-after-emerging-from-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于圣地亚哥的拉美航空集团 (Latam Airlines Group SA) 在退出破产程序 17 个月后，对其财务状况充满信心，将寻求新的交易，并宣称自己“对机遇持开放态度”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/latam-airlines-is-looking-to-grow-after-emerging-from-bankruptcy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通认为，如果收益率攀升，高等级需求将面临回落的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/jpmorgan-sees-risk-of-pullback-from-high-grade-amid-outperformance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通表示，尽管风险溢价仍处于两年多来的最紧水平，但美国高等级债券收益率的攀升可能会导致投资者撤离该资产类别。公司分析师。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/jpmorgan-sees-risk-of-pullback-from-high-grade-amid-outperformance</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 13:55:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>柯林斯认为美联储降息时间比之前预期的要晚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/collins-sees-fed-cutting-later-than-she-previously-thought</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿联邦储备银行行长苏珊·柯林斯表示，她仍然对通胀下降持乐观态度，当前的环境要求对利率保持耐心。柯林斯在彭博电视台接受迈克·麦基采访时还讨论了劳动力市场的状况，并表示美国总统大选“绝对”不会影响降息时机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/collins-sees-fed-cutting-later-than-she-previously-thought</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 13:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
